D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20stock%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bmodest%20to%20disappointing%26quot%3B%20when%20they've%20traded%20at%20%26quot%3Bsimilar%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20multiples%20to%20those%20in%20evidence%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20tricky%20bit%20is%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20when%20trouble%20is%20going%20to%20strike!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d4a5aae-20db-4aa7-8066-545dd112f3b6%5C%22%3EThe%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20ratio's%20pros%20and%20cons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20ratio%20was%20developed%20by%20Nobel%20Prize-winning%20economist%20Robert%20Shiller%2C%20who%20predicted%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20would%20burst%20in%20%26quot%3BIrrational%20Exuberance%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20just%20as%20the%20market%20peaked%20in%20March%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20correctly%20warned%20the%20housing%20boom%20could%20collapse%20in%20the%20book's%20second%20edition%2C%20published%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20use%20the%20traditional%20P%2FE%20ratio%20to%20value%20a%20company's%20stock%20based%20on%20its%20earnings%20multiple%2C%20or%20how%20many%20times%20higher%20its%20price%20is%20than%20its%20earnings%20per%20share%2C%20or%20EPS%2C%20in%20a%20year.%20They%20calculate%20it%20by%20dividing%20a%20stock%20price%20by%20an%20annual%20EPS%20figure%2C%20either%20historical%20or%20projected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20ratio%20takes%20a%20stock%20index's%20point%20value%20and%20divides%20it%20by%20the%20combined%20EPS%20of%20its%20constituent%20companies%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%20and%20divided%20by%2010%20to%20get%20a%20real%2C%20average%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20at%206%2C700%20points%2C%20and%20its%20average%2C%20inflation-adjusted%20EPS%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20is%20%24167%2C%20dividing%20one%20by%20the%20other%20yields%20a%20multiple%20of%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ratio%20can%20smooth%20out%20the%20effects%20of%20business%20cycles%20on%20profits%20by%20factoring%20in%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20earnings%2C%20providing%20a%20longer-term%20perspective%20on%20market%20valuation%20than%20the%20conventional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-pe-ratio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EP%2FE%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20ratio%20doesn't%20indicate%20an%20imminent%20crash%2C%20as%20markets%20can%20remain%20overvalued%20or%20undervalued%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20account%20for%20interest%20rates%2C%20index%20composition%2C%20economic%20shifts%2C%20and%20corporate%20profitability%2C%20which%20can%20vary%20between%20time%20periods%20and%20influence%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230b15306-7f71-48b6-aa52-7ba2fb6177e2%5C%22%3EBubble%20watchers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20doubled%20in%20five%20years%20to%20trade%20at%20record%20highs%2C%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20stocks%20such%20as%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20soared%20almost%2014-fold%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20public%20company%20with%20a%20%244.3%20trillion%20market%20capitalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20commentators%20have%20flagged%20that%20stocks%20are%20pricey.%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-jerome-powell-federal-reserve-chair%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJerome%20Powell%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20speech%20that%20%26quot%3Bequity%20prices%20are%20fairly%20highly%20valued.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErik%20Gordon%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan's%20Ross%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20August%20that%20the%20huge%20market%20values%20and%20vast%20shareholder%20bases%20of%20AI%20companies%20like%20Microsoft%20and%20Meta%20meant%20%26quot%3Bmore%20investors%20will%20suffer%20than%20suffered%20in%20the%20dot-com%20crash%2C%20and%20their%20suffering%20will%20be%20more%20painful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor%20Kevin%20O'Leary%20and%20tech%20investor%20Ross%20Gerber%20dismissed%20the%20comparison%20between%20the%20AI%20boom%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20in%20separate%20interviews%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%20said%20in%20August%20that%20the%20AI%20boom%20isn't%20like%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20because%20%26quot%3Byou%20actually%20can%20see%20the%20productivity%20and%20measure%20it%20on%20a%20dollar-by-dollar%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerber%20said%20that%20valuations%20are%20justified%20because%20AI%20companies%20promise%20tremendous%20growth%20and%20their%20profitability%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20insane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-shiller-pe-ratio-dot-com-bubble-ai-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758725005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d402e5f9db348adc0c114d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-shiller-pe-ratio-dot-com-bubble-ai-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20Shiller%20P%2FE%20ratio%20cleared%2040%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%2C%20when%20it%20preceded%20a%2049%25%20crash%20in%20the%20benchmark%20stock%20index.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40businessinsider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-shiller-pe-ratio-dot-com-bubble-ai-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am