k.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESiemiatkowski%20also%20shared%20a%20message%20from%20the%20chairman%20saying%20Klarna%20is%2010%20years%20behind%20a%20rival.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Klarna's%20big%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-office-return-employee-reaction-emojis-ipo-rto-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemployee%3C%2Fa%3E%20conference%20last%20week%20in%20Stockholm%2C%20CEO%20Sebastian%20Siemiatkowski%20swapped%20spreadsheets%20for%20a%20rap%20performance%20and%20then%20confronted%20a%20sobering%20reality.%20Even%20as%20Klarna%20basks%20in%20its%20%2415%20billion%20IPO%2C%20chairman%20Michael%20Moritz%20warned%20staff%20of%20a%20rival%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%2010%20years%20behind%20Revolut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swedish%20fintech%20gathered%20about%203%2C000%20employees%20in%20Stockholm%20for%20the%20convention%2C%20which%20featured%20keynote%20speeches%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20team-building%20activities%20aimed%20at%20celebrating%20the%20company's%20recent%20milestones%20and%20boosting%20employee%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiemiatkowski%20kicked%20off%20its%20%26quot%3BSmoooth%20week%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20lip-sync%20performance%20of%20a%20rap%20about%20Klarna%2C%20according%20to%20two%20current%20employees%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20since%20they%20were%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Klarna%20chief%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ipo-employee-shares-cash-out-rsu-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecent%20IPO%20milestone%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20flood%20of%20congratulatory%20messages%20he%20had%20received.%20Among%20them%20was%20a%20stark%20text%20message%20from%20chairman%20Michael%20Moritz%2C%20which%20was%20displayed%20on%20a%20screen%20at%20the%20venue%20in%20Stockholm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20displayed%20message%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Moritz%20told%20Siemiatkowski%2C%20%26quot%3BSebastian.%20As%20we%20celebrate%2020%20years%2C%20we%20need%20to%20remember%20we%20are%2010%20years%20behind%20Revolut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frevolut-karma-bonus-system-compliance-workplace-culture-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevolut%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20British%20neo-bank%20with%20over%2052%20million%20customers.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20prepaid%20foreign%20exchange%20card%20has%20rapidly%20grown%20into%20a%20wide-ranging%20financial%20platform%2C%20covering%20everything%20from%20banking%20and%20savings%20to%20investing%2C%20crypto%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20business%20accounts.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20working%20toward%20its%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%20full-service%20global%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Klarna%20is%20a%20licensed%20bank%20in%20Sweden%2C%20its%20activities%20are%20largely%20limited%20to%20payments%20and%20short-term%20lending.%20But%20it%20launched%20a%20US%20debit%20card%20pilot%20in%20June%20to%20venture%20into%20traditional%20banking%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20app%26quot%3B%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20now%20has%20about%20111%20million%20users%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20its%20business%20comes%20from%20the%20merchant-funded%20zero-percent%20interest%20financing%20it%20offers%20customers%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20told%20CNBC%20earlier%20this%20month.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20Klarna%20sees%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20to%20disrupt%20the%20US%20credit%20card%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20went%20public%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20raising%20about%20%241.37%20billion.%20The%20offering%20valued%20the%20Swedish%20fintech%20at%20%2415%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20