0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E's%20AI-powered%20search%20offerings%2C%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20web%20is%20making%20a%20pivotal%20shift%20from%20traditional%20search%20engines%20to%20AI-powered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-microsoft-openai-fight-standards-limit-ai-access-websites-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanswer%20engines%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20create%20responses%20directly%20from%20scraped%20content%2C%20often%20without%20linking%20back%20to%20original%20sources.%20This%20threatens%20the%20web's%20original%20traffic-driven%20model%2C%20which%20rewards%20content%20creation%20with%20clicks%2C%20views%2C%20and%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20AI%20companies%2C%20including%20OpenAI%2C%20have%20separate%20web%20crawling%20bots%20for%20search%20services%20and%20AI%20offerings.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Google's%20main%20search%20bot%20collects%20data%20from%20websites%20to%20feed%20both%20traditional%20search%20results%20and%20new%20AI-powered%20answer%20engines%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-generative-experience-ai-lady-gaga-sge-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20Overviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloudflare's%20new%20bot%20policy%20and%20license%20target%20Google's%20data-scraping%20advantage%20and%20seek%20to%20even%20the%20playing%20field%2C%20said%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatthew-prince-search-engines-ai-cloudflare-google-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Prince%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20AI%20answer%20engine%20should%20have%20to%20play%20by%20the%20same%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20combines%20its%20crawler%20for%20search%20with%20its%20AI%20answer%20engines%2C%20which%20gives%20them%20a%20unique%20and%20unfair%20advantage.%20We%20are%20making%20clear%20that%20there%20are%20now%20different%20rules%20for%20search%20and%20AI%20answer%20engines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229922e788-09f4-41d7-bb0c-49402f5340d4%5C%22%3ECloudflare%20can%20help%20block%20AI%20bot%20crawlers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Content%20Signals%20Policy%2C%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20builds%20on%20the%20company's%20existing%20web%20crawling%20bot%20management%20service%2C%20with%20new%20signals%20specifically%20aimed%20at%20AI%20crawlers%20and%20data%20scrapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWebsites%20use%20a%20standard%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-ai-ignore-rule-scraping-web-contect-robotstxt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobots.txt%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20control%20how%20bots%20access%20their%20data.%20This%C2%A0system%20was%20established%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20web.%20Now%2C%20the%20boom%20in%20AI%20bot%20scraping%20is%20putting%20pressure%20on%20it.%20Essentially%2C%20it's%20a%20gentlemen's%20agreement%2C%20and%20some%20AI%20companies%20ignore%20these%20website%20preferences%20and%20still%20crawl%20sites%20for%20data%20because%20their%20thirst%20for%20it%20is%20so%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%203.8%20million%20domains%20already%20use%20Cloudflare's%20robots.txt%20service.%20Cloudflare%20is%20introducing%20what%20is%20essentially%20a%20new%20license%20for%20websites%20to%20help%20them%20explicitly%20block%20or%20allow%20AI%20bot%20crawlers%20in%20nuanced%20and%20more%20powerful%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d814eae3-9154-42ca-a7c7-6c461ccaac9f%5C%22%3EWhat%20this%20means%20for%20Google%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20said%20this%20license%20could%20carry%20legal%20weight%2C%20especially%20for%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle's%20legal%20team%20will%20see%20this%20for%20what%20it%20is%20%E2%80%94%20a%20contract%20with%20legal%20ramifications%20if%20they%20ignore%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20P