the%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20said%20that%20OpenAI%20is%20being%20more%20responsible%20here%20by%20separating%20out%20its%20crawling%20bots%2C%20having%20one%20for%20its%20core%20AI%20operations%20and%20another%20for%20search%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1e0df5d-4240-4908-8790-7c41b7a98f73%5C%22%3EUsers%20have%20more%20control%20over%20AI%20bots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECloudflare's%20new%20tool%20allows%20creators%20to%20clearly%20express%20preferences%20about%20how%20their%20content%20may%20be%20used%2C%20choosing%20either%20%26quot%3BYes%26quot%3B%20content%20can%20be%20used%20or%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B%20content%20should%20not%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20policy%20distinguishes%20between%20different%20AI-related%20uses%2C%20including%20search%2C%20AI%20input%2C%20and%20AI%20training%2C%20and%20it%20reminds%20crawlers%20that%20robots.txt%20declarations%20can%20carry%20%26quot%3Blegal%20significance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20search%20preference%20would%20tell%20bot%20crawlers%20that%20a%20site's%20content%20can%20only%20be%20scraped%20for%20use%20in%20traditional%20search%20engines%20that%20send%20users%20to%20the%20original%20source%20of%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20input%20preference%20covers%20increasingly%20common%20situations%20where%20AI%20chatbots%20and%20AI%20models%20roam%20the%20web%20and%20collect%20website%20data%20for%20immediate%20summarization%20and%20inclusion%20in%20AI%20outputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20preference%2C%20AI%20training%2C%20would%20allow%20websites%20to%20block%20AI%20bots%20that%20scrape%20data%20for%20use%20in%20the%20initial%20pre-training%20process%2C%20in%20which%20AI%20models%20are%20trained%20to%20understand%20the%20world%20in%20broad%20and%20powerful%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20the%20web%20remains%20open%20and%20thriving%2C%20we're%20giving%20website%20owners%20a%20better%20way%20to%20express%20how%20companies%20are%20allowed%