D%20Dolphin%20Surf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d2b414183847aa39d7490d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221123%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBYD%20launched%20its%20ultra-affordable%20Dolphin%20Surf%20city%20car%20in%20Europe%20earlier%20this%20year.%3Cp%3ERafael%20Eduardo%20Wefers%20Ver%C3%A1stegui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20we%20went%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-car-ev-road-trip-toyota-bz4x-genesis-gv60-charging-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20roadtrip%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Spain%20to%20Germany%20to%20visit%20family.%20We%20were%20traveling%20with%20our%20two%20small%20dogs%2C%20and%20our%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntially%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20take%20the%20Dolphin%20Surf%20and%20an%20RV%20up%20to%20the%20Pyranees%2C%20and%20then%20park%20the%20BYD%20and%20take%20the%20RV%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way%20to%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Bordeaux%2C%20the%20RV's%20engine%20broke%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20take%20it%20back%20to%20the%20garage%20where%20the%20Dolphin%20Surf%20was%20parked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20wanted%20to%20visit%20our%20family%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20throw%20away%20our%20vacation%20plans%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20%26quot%3Bscrew%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20switched%20from%20an%20RV%20to%20a%20small%20compact%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b927939-7d99-4453-be73-981eeae41786%5C%22%3E1%2C000-mile%20test%20drive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20was%20very%20cautious%20and%20decided%20against%20relying%20on%20the%20built%20in%20navigation%20system%2C%20instead%20just%20charging%20when%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20needed%20too.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20I'd%20crossed%20the%20French%20border%2C%20I%20had%20a%20good%20feeling%20for%20the%20total%20range%20of%20the%20car%2C%20and%20felt%20relaxed%20about%20charging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20would%20drive%20for%20two%20to%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20and%20then%20have%20a%20break.%20If%20you%20have%20two%20small%20dogs%20plus%20two%20people%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20need%20to%20have%20regular%20bathroom%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20charging%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d2b4ec57d362d375e8ad87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBYD%20Dolphin%20Surf%20at%20a%20charging%20station.%3Cp%3ERafael%20Eduardo%20Wefers%20Ver%C3%A1stegui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20drove%20through%20the%20night.%20I%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20a%20little%20power%20nap%20while%20the%20car%20was%20charging%2C%20which%20was%20always%20done%20within%2030%20to%2040%20minutes%2C%20even%20when%20the%20battery%20was%20below%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20the%20journey%20in%2022%20hours.%20With%20a%20gasoline%20car%2C%20I%20would%20usually%20take%2018.%20The%20extra%20four%20hours%20allowed%20me%20to%20take%20regular%20power%20naps%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20do%20before%20when%20I%20drove%20a%20gasoline%20car%2C%20and%20I%20arrived%20more%20relaxed%20and%20without%20range%20anxiety.%20The%20overall%20trip%20was%20very%20pleasant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20of%20driving%20over%201%2C600%20kilometers%20(994%20miles)%20was%20so%20good%20that%20when%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20a%20car%20too%2C%20we%20went%20for%20a%20BYD%20again%2C%20buying%20the%20larger%20Dolphin%20hatchback%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c761903-9ae5-4679-b221-fa39b18350d4%5C%22%3EBYD%20rolls%20into%20Europe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20our%20first%20EVs%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20huge%20difference%20compared%20to%20driving%20a%20gasoline%20car.%20With%20an%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20you%20have%20to%20think%20about%20hot%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ev-batteries-drain-faster-dont-last-long-cold-weather-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D