der%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20treat%20each%20unit%20as%20if%20it's%20its%20own%20miniature%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Florida-based%20couple%20started%20buying%20rentals%20in%202020%20to%20create%20an%20additional%20revenue%20stream%20and%20accelerate%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-generate-passive-income-portfolio-coworking-office-space-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogress%20toward%20financial%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20of%202025%2C%20they%20own%2028%20units%20across%2015%20commercial%20and%20residential%20properties%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20confirmed%20through%20the%20Brevard%20County%20Property%20Appraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20average%20cash-on-cash%20return%20is%20just%20north%20of%2020%25%2C%20said%20Ted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20guarantee%20immediate%20cash%20flow%2C%20they've%20narrowed%20down%20their%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20box%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20set%20of%20criteria%20they've%20established%20that%20they%20want%20to%20see%20in%20a%20property%20before%20purchasing.%20Here's%20exactly%20what%20they're%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Properties%20in%20their%20backyard.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Garbers%2C%20who%20live%20on%20the%20east%20coast%20of%20Florida%20in%20Brevard%20County%2C%20like%20to%20keep%20their%20investment%20properties%20close%20to%20home%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20still%20focused%20on%20our%20backyard.%20It's%20still%20appreciating.%20It's%20still%20in%20high%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ted%2C%20who%20manages%20each%20of%20their%2015%20properties.%20While%20they'd%20eventually%20like%20to%20expand%20to%20different%20markets%2C%20there%20is%20enough%20opportunity%20on%20the%20Space%20Coast%20to%20keep%20them%20busy%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Affordability.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BOur%20buy%20box%20is%20affordable%20housing%20%E2%80%94%20not%