ssible%20is%20because%20the%20mammals%20now%20share%20the%20ground%20with%20people%20and%20their%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20demarcate%20the%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20push%20for%20them%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20protected%20zones%2C%20Menon%20says%2C%20they%20relied%20on%20elephant%20footpaths.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20mapped%20these%20and%20showed%20it%20in%20a%20publication%2C%20explaining%20why%20they%20were%20integral%20pieces%20of%20land%20that%20connected%20with%20the%20different%20habitats.%20We%20delineated%20these%20on%20paper%2C%20asking%20the%20Government%20to%20protect%20these%20elephant%20corridors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20learnings%20they%20had%20during%20the%20project%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20protection%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20can%20be%20done%20in%20four%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20model%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20the%20community%20model%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20focuses%20on%20land%20being%20kept%20aside%20by%20the%20community%20for%20elephants%20to%20move.%20It%20also%20involves%20rewarding%20the%20community%20with%20some%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20model%20is%20pushing%20the%20Government%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20conduct%20linear%20infrastructure%20mitigations.%20The%20third%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180063%2Fkerala-woman-animal-rights-elephants-inspirational%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20community%20of%20people%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20trained%20in%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20elephant%20movements.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20there%20are%20groups%20of%20young%20boys%20who%20are%20on%20alert.%20They%20stop%20cars%20to%20allow%20the%20elephants%20to%20cross.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20is%20to%20relocate%20villages.%20This%20%E2%80%9Clast-ditch%20effort%E2%80%9D%20is%20only%20resorted%20to%20in%20areas%20where%20people%20have%20settled%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20elephants%20are%20killing%20them%20and%20not%20letting%20crops%20grow%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-223x300.jpg%20223w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-768x1033.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1142x1536.jpg%201142w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1523x2048.jpg%201523w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1200x1614.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-150x202.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescue%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%20when%20Menon%20and%20his%20team%20started%20the%20rescue%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20orphan%20elephant%20calves%20to%20reintroduce%20them%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20people%20discouraged%20the%20idea.%20But%20the%20conservationist%20points%20to%20the%2050%20percent%20success%20rate%20they%20have%20achieved%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20their%20persistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPutting%20policies%20in%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Menon%20received%20the%20Whitley%20Award%20for%20a%20project%20focusing%20on%20%E2%80%98Monitoring%20of%20Elephant%20Poaching%20and%20Ivory%20Trade%20in%20India%20and%20Asia%E2%80%99.%20Reaching%20this%20zenith%20of%20excellence%20gave%20tremendous%20backing%20to%20his%20work%20in%20putting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190973%2Findia-first-wildlife-underpass-kanha-pench-corridor-tigers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20corridors%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20earmarked%20the%20Sigur%20Plateau%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sees%20the%20movement%20of%20around%206%2C300%20Asiatic%20Elephants%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%2C%20%3Cem%3EWhitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%20how%20the%20apex%20court%20used%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20evidence%20of%20the%20benefits%20to%20both%20wildlife%20and%20people.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20created%20ripples%3B%20shaping%20the%20crux%20of%20wildlife%20policies%20as%20we%20speak.%3C